{"tid":10070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG其實同高登仲有其他forum有根本上既唔同","createTime":"2016-11-28T20:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T20:28:50.000Z","uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2136ec059634c00e18a12c0459cf484db8f932","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:14:00.000Z","msg":"LIHKG算係第一個發源於手機既討論區，所有user都係手機user<br />\n<br />\n其實大家可以將LIHKG睇成為一個容納咗幾萬人嘅whatsapp group, 每個post為一個subgroup, 大家可以暢所欲言, 分享圖片 等等, 唔似其他討論區多多管制俾人控制和諧化<br />\n<br />\n今次呢個&quot;group&quot;開得成我哋一定要好好珍惜同埋好好運用呢個好處，大家要記緊要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b644d6037dad484d8c38244f3ab5db97f056c99c","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:19:28.000Z","msg":"我有一個propose,<br />\n<br />\n平時whatsapp group突然比人拉左入去或都自願選入左去，咁你係個group入面講嘅所有野全部算係private talk, 呢一個concept我唔可以帶來LIHKG上面, 令我哋可以避過某啲法律審查白色恐怖，從而minimise個法律責任，令大家言論更自由？"},{"pid":"395b621e1bde26c490231203aae25867efb9fbed","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:21:39.000Z","msg":"但前提可能係，唔可以有一個website domain做基地，或者其實冇必要。但就可以好似whsapp, line咁出web 版"},{"pid":"c8d79265a3eedb92d242846094f72bb2e1363d4c","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:22:23.000Z","msg":"有冇法律界人士幫手諗諗？"},{"pid":"ec75967b30a5a82a4ca461133fc6400f7029c50f","tid":10070,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇法律界人士幫手諗諗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個concept 都幾複雜<br />\nBetween 香港冇左法治架喇<br />\n法律問題其實諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想做就做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df475a25fbc9fed800bbd5abbc0957c37770bc5d","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:25:25.000Z","msg":"同埋可能唔可以用討論區自稱<br />\n<br />\n或者LIHKG應該係改革左討論區呢個概念<br />\n<br />\n係一個進化"},{"pid":"7b3c0f9374bb1980e6cdcc538c1c4ffcb8f3cd4f","tid":10070,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:27:17.000Z","msg":"我相信會有人明我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbe7445123ca9e0ec063fb0c5156a0aa20bb856","tid":10070,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:28:50.000Z","msg":"g持!"}]}